column55: FULLY FURNISHED single family home rental is available for IMMEDIATE move-in. This charming residence offers 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a perfect blend of comfort, style, and a touch of whimsy. Inside, you'll discover a spacious living room, ideal for hosting gatherings or relaxation. The fully equipped kitchen, complete with modern appliances sets the stage for memorable meals and entertaining friends. The bedrooms are thoughtfully furnished to create cozy retreats, while the beautifully appointed bathrooms offer a touch of luxury. Step outside to find a well-maintained front yard that adds to the property's curb appeal, and a backyard oasis that beckons for socializing, barbecues, and enjoying the Florida sunshine. With a private circular driveway and garage, parking is a breeze no more searching for spots. Located mere steps from the heart of downtown Gulfport. Explore charming shops, discover renowned restaurants, and immerse yourself in the local arts and culture scene. Don't forget about the nearby picturesque waterfront, offering breathtaking sunsets, beach activities, and opportunities to embrace an active coastal lifestyle. Power, sewer, water, trash, cable TV, wifi, lawn care, and pest control are all included. Pets welcome. Call today and make the "Gecko House" your summer and/or fall home!

column86: Bring your funky vibe to the progressive, artsy community of Gulfport. This  charming two bedroom, two bath, one car garage colorful charmer is  located just a quick walk to the waterfront marina dotted with bobbing  sailboats and floating pelicans as well as the historic downtown area on  Boca Ciega Bay. Pull in to your circular drive way surrounded by an easy to  maintain xeriscaped yard. Upon entering your art deco home, you will feel  hugged by warmth and peacefulness. From the entry foyer, head to the  dining area with a wall of windows welcoming in the Florida sunshine. A  modern, classy kitchen is designed with marbled granite counters, built in  wine rack, wine fridge and a convenient pass through window. The  bathrooms are immaculate, keeping the vintage feel alive while the  bedrooms are cozy. Vacation in your own backyard paradise on the  covered patio engulfed in tropical bamboo. Saunter along the paved paths  through colorful plants in your ample, fenced outdoor garden. Schedule  your private tour today!
